  "htmlContent": "<h2>Meeting Agenda</h2>\n<img src=\"ncgicc-logo-00d2d1b6-6e23-4446-823e-42b9d1d4e9ae.png\" alt=\"NCGICC Logo\" width=\"109\" height=\"100\" />\n<h2 id=\"heading-1\">North Carolina GEOGRAPHIC INFORMATION COORDINATING COUNCIL</h2>\n<h2 id=\"heading-2\">AGENDA</h2>\n<p>August 10, 2016 1:00 pm - 3:00 pm\nEducation Building, Room 755, 301 N. Wilmington St., Raleigh, North Carolina</p>\n<table><caption>Meeting Agenda Details</caption><thead><tr><th><strong>TIME</strong></th><th><strong>AGENDA ITEM</strong></th><th><strong>GICC MEMBER or GUEST</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1 min.</td><td>1. Welcome</td><td>Stan Duncan, Chair</td></tr><tr><td>8 min.</td><td>2. Chair Announcements</td><td>Stan Duncan</td></tr><tr><td>1 min.</td><td>3. Approval of Minutes of May 11th Meeting</td><td>Stan Duncan</td></tr><tr><td>10 min.</td><td>4. Progress on Statewide IT Activities</td><td>John Correllus</td></tr><tr><td>30 min.</td><td>5. AddressNC and Census 2020</td><td>Joe Sewash and Bob Coats</td></tr><tr><td>15 min.</td><td>6. NextGen911 in NC</td><td>Richard Taylor</td></tr><tr><td>20 min.</td><td>7. Working Group for PLS and GIS</td><td>Bob Brinson</td></tr><tr><td>20 min.</td><td>8. Committee Reports\n\u2022 Statewide Mapping Advisory Committee\n  o Vote: Standard for Parcel Data Content (Summary)\n\u2022 Local Government\n  o Vote: LGC Bylaws Revised\n\u2022 State Government GIS Users\n\u2022 Federal Interagency\n\u2022 Technical Advisory\n\u2022 Management &amp; Operations</td><td>Ryan Draughn\nKathryn Clifton\nJohn Farley\nDoug Newcomb\nDan Madding\nStan Duncan</td></tr><tr><td>5 min.</td><td>9. Statewide Orthoimagery Program</td><td>Tim Johnson</td></tr><tr><td>5 min.</td><td>10. NC OneMap Update</td><td>David Giordano</td></tr><tr><td>5 min.</td><td>11. GICC Member Announcements</td><td>All</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3 id=\"heading-3\">2016 NC GICC Meeting Dates</h3>\n<p>Wednesday, November 9\n\n(New) GICC Website: <a href=\"http://it.nc.gov/gicc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://it.nc.gov/gicc</a></p>",
